Allow for zoom parameter in Editor (#353)

This allows for a zoom paramter be passed into the `PL.Editor` method.

```
 editor = new PL.Editor({
          mapModule: true,
          lat: 23,
          lon: 77,
	  zoom: 5
});
```

Continues https://github.com/publiclab/plots2/issues/6804
